    "text_instructions": [
      {
        "id": "01f10ef331ef19a3a5aa43f71308ca6f",
        "content": [
          "### Tables Guide\r\n",
          "**bi_output_vg_club_offers**: Use for questions about club benefits, offers, eligibility, claiming, activation, and cancellations. Each row is one user × one offer.\r\n",
          "**bi_output_vg_club**: Use for questions involving deposit/withdrawal amounts, revenue, invested amounts, transaction counts, or equity breakdown (RealizedEquityClub, eMoneyBalance, etc). This has more granular financial data.\r\n",
          "**bi_output_vg_revenue**: Use for questions regrding revenue and the different revenue metrics\r\n",
          "**bi_output_vg_mimo**: Use for questions regarding deposit withdraw\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "## Query Guidelines\r\n",
          "1. When asked about \"club members\" or \"club users\", query from bi_output_vg_club. For \"current\" status, always filter to the most recent Date available: `WHERE Date = (SELECT MAX(Date) FROM bi_output_vg_club)`.\r\n",
          "2. When counting users, always use COUNT(DISTINCT RealCID) or COUNT(DISTINCT CID) to avoid duplicates.\r\n",
          "3. When asked about \"offers\" or \"benefits\", use bi_output_vg_club_offers. Active offers have Active=true. Claimed offers have AssetStatus='Claimed'. Cancelled offers have CancellationDate IS NOT NULL.\r\n",
          "4. Always create CTE for every table and then join on requested timeframe and dimensions\r\n",
          "5. WHEN data and measures are  taken from bi_output_vg_aum THEN based on timeframe, WHEN asked for weekly THEN filter on IsLastDayWeek = 1,WHEN asked for monthly THEN filter on IsLastDayMonth=1,WHEN asked for quarterly THEN filter on IsLastDayQuarter = 1 WHEN asked for Yearly THEN filter on IsLastDayYear = 1\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "## Date/Time Guidelines\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "* last week should be interpreted as the last 7 days\r\n",
          "* Last month should be interpreted as the last 30 days\r\n",
          "* last last year should be interpreted as the last 12 month\r\n",
          "* first day of week is always sunday\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "\r\n"
        ]
      }
    ],
